Invocation Name: the voice for real estate
des: The Voice for Real Estate is the National Association of REALTORS®' video news series. Every two weeks, host Stephen Gasque, NAR's Director of Broadcasting and Multimedia Communications, shines a spotlight on the top legislative, regulatory, legal and research topics NAR is working on, in support of its members, homeownership and property investment across America.
